msgctxt "Languages::ab__ab.help.create_banner.title"
msgid "ab__ab.help.create_banner.title"
msgstr "Creating of advanced banner"

msgctxt "Languages::ab__ab.help.create_banner.text"
msgid "ab__ab.help.create_banner.text"
msgstr ""
"<ol>"
"    <li>Create a new banner (Marketing / Banners [+]);</li>"
"    <li>Specify the Name, Position and the Type of the banner - AB: Advanced;</li>"
"    <li>If you want to use a composite banner, which consists of a background and image (for example, the advertised product), then upload a product photo (previously preparing a product image: trim background and adjust to the desired size);</li>"
"    <li>Specify the color scheme of the banner. If the banner is light, choose a dark scheme (all texts will be black). If the banner will be dark, select light scheme (all texts will be white);</li>"
"    <li>Enter the Title and Description of your offer. You can use html-tags;</li>"
"    <li>Enter the text for the button on the banner by click on which will be a transition (eg, <b>I'm interested</b>). If left blank, the button will not be displayed and the entire area of the banner will be link;</li>"
"    <li>Decide for yourself, whether to use a background image, or simply specify a background color for a more economical using of resources. Loaded background image will fill the entire area of the banner, will be automatically centered on mobile devices;</li>"
"    <li>Provide a link to the advertised content, and you can set the checkbox to open the link in a new page;</li>"
"    <li>Save the banner;</li>"
"</ol>"

msgctxt "Languages::ab__ab.help.show_banner.title"
msgid "ab__ab.help.show_banner.title"
msgstr "Creating a block for the advanced banner"

msgctxt "Languages::ab__ab.help.show_banner.text"
msgid "ab__ab.help.show_banner.text"
msgstr ""
"<ol>"
"    <li>Create or select the appropriate section in the layouts (go to Administration panel - Design - Layouts) and create in it a new block with type <b>Banner</b> (You can use an already created a banner block);</li>"
"    <li>When you add block <b>Banner</b> specify the Name and Type (AB: Carousel (Advanced) or AB: Advanced) and click the link that appears (Settings).</li>"
"    <li>Specify the desired settings for banner display;</li>"
"    <li>After completing the settings, go to the Content tab and select a previously created by you AB: Advanced banner or banners, if you are using AB: Carousel (Advanced);</li>"
"    <li>Save block;</li>"
"</ol>"